	   <tr><td colspan=2><br>  Two of my friends and myself are going to start a group on eq. We r not sure if we are going to do pvp or not. One of us will definately be a warrior and I think one will be a shaman rather that a cleric(possibly a druid). What I need to know is what class should the 3rd person be?<br>We want it to be mostly fun.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
