	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ogres have the best ratings  strength, stamina, etc., followed by Trolls. Despite this, Trolls also get regeneration. This makes both races extremely lethal warriors, but they have severe experience penalties, plus they are hated in nearly every city. That is a big disadvantage. Halflings and Humans are decent as well, because they are basically the opposite: they have good faction, and experience bonuses. They are lacking in ratings tho. Dwarves are basically the best rounded out warrior, since they have no xp penalty, decent ratings, good faction, and great vision. In the end it depends on your love of the game. If you are an eq addict and play constantly, Trolls and Ogres are who to be. If you have more of a life then the rest of us, be a Halfling or Human. If you decide to be a mesh between the two extremes, be a Dwarf or a Barbarian. (Barbarians have traits of the two extremes) And no other race is really worth being a warrior<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
