	   <tr><td colspan=2>All races are balanced. They all have their pros and cons. Pick the one YOU would be most comfortable playing and the one with which you will have the most FUN playing. Geez, IMHO, 99% of all warrior guides I see out on the suggest being a Barbarian/Troll/Ogre. Its not like the other smaller races don't have their good points. Like Halflings/Gnomes/Elves...They have nice agility and dex that would help procs and AC. Isn't AC the most important thing for warriors?<br>And Humans and Half Elves....Wouldn't it be nice to have decent strength/sta/agi/dex and still have enough INT to keep your various skills maxed? Whatever race you choose, make sure its a race you will have fun playing, not a race that OTHERS have fun playing. Experiment with all of them if you have to. You might as well get the most out of the 10 bucks your paying every month.<br><br><br>Azuden Stormblade<br>Level 21 Half Elf Warrior<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
