	   <tr><td colspan=2>The biggest drawback with low Strength is that you will be limited in what you can carry. You will have to be careful about the type of armour you wear so that you don't get too weighed down, but there are plenty of items around that are light weight. Look especially for the No Drop items, they will probably be in dungeons far above your level, but since they are No Drop other people often let you loot them. Like the other poster said, keep an eye out for items that add to your stats. You will probably want to increase your Agi and you Str when you get a chance. Check out the Equipment section for ideas on what kind of Armour and Jewellery you will want to acquire.<br>&nbsp;<br>________<br><br>I've travelled this world and have seen many wondrous things. You are not one of them.</td></tr>
